 <H1>Model Issues</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>issues addressed by a hypermedia model
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>document specification
<UL>
<LI>information to recreate the presentation on a other platforms and to
ensure that future systems can interpret the information.
There are 4 items discussed.
<UL>
<LI>media items, structure, presentation, and interaction 
</UL></ul>
<LI>document transportation
<UL>
<LI>not part of the scope of model, but influences the translation of
model to some language expressing the model
</UL><LI>information representation
</UL></UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>hypermedia Vs multimedia  
</H2>
<UL>
<font color=red>
<LI>hypermedia is a collection of multimedia presentations
<LI>multimedia is a collection of media items related temporally and/or
spatially </UL></UL></P>
</font>
